{"tid":1741003,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（自衛術）一人一個比人捉住時逃脫嘅方法","createTime":"2019-11-20T06:58:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-20T06:59:56.000Z","uid":67814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2662cfb2a6e3dcda0defa93044b9a042175f0eb6","tid":1741003,"uid":67814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T06:58:28.000Z","msg":"為咗防止俾人非法禁錮，應該可以點樣還擊<br />\n<br />\n其中一個方法，一俾人拉住，一個反手批踭落塊面到應該即刻縮<br />\n<br />\n或者出撩陰腿，再猴子偷桃<br />\n<br />\n大家仲有咩高見<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db51f8dfb9fb89751c9a6d931bc2e0254be8da2b","tid":1741003,"uid":285694,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T06:59:25.000Z","msg":"有咩招數就同自己身邊啲人講啦<br />\n咁樣自己口爆有撚用咩<br />\n人哋咪又準備好晒點樣應付你🤒"},{"pid":"f98b7f451380525e0c1d214b354f058d54724721","tid":1741003,"uid":285694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T06:59:56.000Z","msg":"人哋塊面有個罩罩着<br />\n你車落去隻手斷都得啦"}]}